title: The Doll of Satan (1969 Horror) Italian film directed by Ferruccio Casapinta

sources.title: The Doll of Satan (1969 Horror) Italian film directed by Ferruccio Casapinta
sources.description:
Elizabeth inherits a spooky old castle from her late uncle. Strange occurrences and ghostly sightings begin to haunt her and her fiancé. As they delve deeper into the castle's secrets, they uncover a dangerous plot by a group of people who want to steal the castle's hidden treasure.

Original title: La bambola di Satana (1969) 
Alternative titles: Satan's Doll, Der Satan ohne Gesicht, La Poupée de Satan, 撒旦的木偶, A Sátán babája

Watch the (Members Only) uncensored version: https://youtu.be/i30nLdb0UXY


Director: Ferruccio Casapinta
Writers: Ferruccio Casapinta, Giorgio Cristallini, Carlo M. Lori
Stars: Erna Schürer, Roland Carey, Aurora Battista
Genre: Italian cinema, Giallo, Horror
